{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/k8s/cka-security/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Heeye Blog","author":"heeye","siteUrl":"https://heeyeah.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"heeyeah/heeyeah.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"heeyeah"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"1142b608-35eb-59cf-84d2-4f918b43dc7f","excerpt":"📌Security TLS 비대칭키를 사용하여 ssl 통신을 하게 되는데, 원리는 이렇다. client와 server가 있을 때 client는 private key를 가지고 있다. server 또한 자신의 private key와 public key를 가지고 있다. server는 먼저 자신의 public key를 보내고(여기서 certificate를 같이 보냄), client는 자신의 private key+server의 public key로 암호화해서 보내며, server…","html":"<h2 id=\"security\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#security\" aria-label=\"security permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📌Security</h2>\n<h3 id=\"tls\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tls\" aria-label=\"tls permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>TLS</h3>\n<p>비대칭키를 사용하여 ssl 통신을 하게 되는데, 원리는 이렇다.</p>\n<p>client와 server가 있을 때</p>\n<p>client는 private key를 가지고 있다.</p>\n<p>server 또한 자신의 private key와 public key를 가지고 있다.</p>\n<p>server는 먼저 자신의 public key를 보내고(여기서 certificate를 같이 보냄), client는 자신의 private key+server의 public key로 암호화해서 보내며,</p>\n<p>server는 자신이 가진 private key로 그걸 푼다. 그러면 client의 private key를 가지겠찌?!</p>\n<p>그때부터 client는 자신의 데이터를 private key로 암호화해서 보내고, server는 받은 private key로 암호를 풀어서 읽는당!</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"concept\"\n        title=\"concept\"\n        src=\"/static/fae7293245f53dedc1becc821521ea71/c1b63/ssl-process.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fae7293245f53dedc1becc821521ea71/5a46d/ssl-process.png 300w,\n/static/fae7293245f53dedc1becc821521ea71/0a47e/ssl-process.png 600w,\n/static/fae7293245f53dedc1becc821521ea71/c1b63/ssl-process.png 1200w,\n/static/fae7293245f53dedc1becc821521ea71/6b26f/ssl-process.png 1658w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>public key 명명규칙 (일반적으로)</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>*.crt</li>\n<li>*.pem</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>private key 명명규칙 (일반적으로)</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>*.key</li>\n<li>*-key.pem</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"tls-in-k8s\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tls-in-k8s\" aria-label=\"tls in k8s permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>TLS in k8s</h4>\n<p>Cert 컨셉\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"concept\"\n        title=\"concept\"\n        src=\"/static/a1b02868fad88c81861f8cd74418360a/c1b63/cert-concept.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a1b02868fad88c81861f8cd74418360a/5a46d/cert-concept.png 300w,\n/static/a1b02868fad88c81861f8cd74418360a/0a47e/cert-concept.png 600w,\n/static/a1b02868fad88c81861f8cd74418360a/c1b63/cert-concept.png 1200w,\n/static/a1b02868fad88c81861f8cd74418360a/6568d/cert-concept.png 1660w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>전체적인 k8s 내부 컴포넌트의 client, server 관계\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"concept\"\n        title=\"concept\"\n        src=\"/static/e4c3b9ade32e611682c4dd7643ba23b4/c1b63/k8s-component-cert.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e4c3b9ade32e611682c4dd7643ba23b4/5a46d/k8s-component-cert.png 300w,\n/static/e4c3b9ade32e611682c4dd7643ba23b4/0a47e/k8s-component-cert.png 600w,\n/static/e4c3b9ade32e611682c4dd7643ba23b4/c1b63/k8s-component-cert.png 1200w,\n/static/e4c3b9ade32e611682c4dd7643ba23b4/9eaa0/k8s-component-cert.png 1676w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>client certificates for clients와 server certificates for servers 분류\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"concept\"\n        title=\"concept\"\n        src=\"/static/72e0e671d17322ef4c5e5a52043594f2/c1b63/client-server-cert.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/72e0e671d17322ef4c5e5a52043594f2/5a46d/client-server-cert.png 300w,\n/static/72e0e671d17322ef4c5e5a52043594f2/0a47e/client-server-cert.png 600w,\n/static/72e0e671d17322ef4c5e5a52043594f2/c1b63/client-server-cert.png 1200w,\n/static/72e0e671d17322ef4c5e5a52043594f2/569c6/client-server-cert.png 1674w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"view-certificates\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#view-certificates\" aria-label=\"view certificates permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>View Certificates</h3>\n<p>cert 정보 확인하는 command\n<code class=\"language-text\">openssl x509 -in /etc/kubernetes/pki/apiserver.crt -text -noout</code></p>\n<p>udemy에서 제공한 kubernetes-cert-checker.xlsx 파일 참고할 것</p>\n<h3 id=\"certificates-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#certificates-api\" aria-label=\"certificates api permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Certificates API</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>CertificateSigningRequest Object</li>\n<li>Review Requests</li>\n<li>Approve Requests</li>\n<li>Shard Certs to Users</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"kubeconfig\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#kubeconfig\" aria-label=\"kubeconfig permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>KubeConfig</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">$HOME/.kube/config</code></p>\n<p>아래에 server나 client key, client cert 이런 정보가 있기 때문에 우린 굳이 커맨드 칠 때 다 안써도 되는 것이다.</p>\n<p><em>Clusters + Users => Contexts</em></p>\n<p>예를 들어 <code class=\"language-text\">Admin@Production (User@Cluster)</code></p>\n<p>컨피그 볼 수 있음 (clusters, contexts, users 정보들)\n<code class=\"language-text\">kubectl config view</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"rbac\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#rbac\" aria-label=\"rbac permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>RBAC</h3>\n<p>Role Binding Access Control으로, role을 정해놓고 user에 할당해서, 권한을 주는 것!</p>\n<h3 id=\"cluster-roles-and-role-bindings\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cluster-roles-and-role-bindings\" aria-label=\"cluster roles and role bindings permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Cluster Roles and Role Bindings</h3>\n<p>Role인데, Cluser 단위 - namespace에 속하지 않음.</p>\n<h3 id=\"image-security\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#image-security\" aria-label=\"image security permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Image Security</h3>\n<p>..?  </p>\n<h3 id=\"security-contexts\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#security-contexts\" aria-label=\"security contexts permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Security Contexts</h3>\n<p>..?</p>\n<h3 id=\"network-policy\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#network-policy\" aria-label=\"network policy permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Network Policy</h3>\n<p>pod 기준으로 트래픽이 들어오는 걸 ingress, 나가는걸 egress라고 함.</p>\n<p>Network Policy는 k8s 리소스 중에 하나임.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"[CKA] Section7. Security","date":"August 01, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/k8s/cka-security/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/k8s/cka-cluster-maintenance/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[CKA] Section6. Cluster Maintenance","category":"k8s","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/k8s/cka-storage/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[CKA] Section8. Storage","category":"k8s","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","521680639"]}